      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(4) The flrstfruit also of thy corn.—See Numbers 18:12. The first of the wool is mentioned here only. The quantity in all these cases has been defined by the Rabbis, on grounds somewhat arbitrary.",
        "children": [
